Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:55.58,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一定是这样  当数不清的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:23:00.58,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}全部如愿之后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.00,0:23:05.68,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我们还会贪婪地没有休止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.93,0:23:09.96,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}直到开始后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.09,0:23:12.61,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}永远过不够的昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.61,0:23:15.00,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}和不断积蓄的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.00,0:23:20.72,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就这样重叠着伴我前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.04,0:23:26.93,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}能够成为非常喜欢的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:32.00,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}非常喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:37.16,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}连这样的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.30,0:23:41.90,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我还无法完全相信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.90,0:23:46.60,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}总是难以如愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.76,0:23:52.32,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}多想再长高一些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.38,0:23:54.70,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}愿我可以笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.77,0:23:57.18,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}用幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.25,0:24:00.42,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}为明天
